#flex内容总结

```Html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
<link rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' href='flexbox style.css'>
</head>

<body>
    <div class='container'>
        <div class='item'>Item 1</div>
        <div class='item'>Item 2</div>
        <div class='item'>Item 3</div>
        <div class='item'>Item 4</div>
        <div class='item'>Item 5</div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
```

```CSS
.container {
    background: cornflowerblue;
    width: 500px;
    height: 300px;
    /*border: 1px solid black;*/
    /*-----------Start-------------------------------------*/
    /*display: inline;*/
    display: flex;
    /*上边为display定义为弹性盒子*/
    flex-direction: row;
    /*主轴方向朝哪*/
    justify-content: center;
    /*主轴上怎样显示'flex-start'*/
    align-items: stretch;
    /*副轴上怎样显示全containor充满 或者 ‘flex-start’*/
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    /*能否换行显示，默认值是不能nowrap*/
    /*---以上均为flex的containor级属性----*/
    /*-----------Over--------------------------------------*/
}

.item {
    background-color: lightgrey;
    /*float: right;*/
    /*display: block;*/
    width: 101px;
    height: 20px;
    margin: auto;
}


/*.item1 {*/


/*    background-color: lightgrey;*/


/*float: right;*/


/*display: block;*/


/*    font-size:2em;*/


/*    width: 100px;*/


/*    height: 50px;*/


/*    margin: 10px;*/


/*align-self:flex-start;*/


/*}*/

```
